                                                            veritatis,
                                                            consequatur, porro rerum dolorem quas
                                                        </p>
                                                    </article>
                                                </article>

                                            </section>
                                        </article>
                                    </section>
                                </article>
                            </section>
                        }
                    </section>

                    <hr>


                    <!-- quotes Section STarts -->
                    <section class="quotesPartsStarts">

                        <section>
                            <section class="eachquotesSection">
                                <section class="row">

                                    <article class="col-5">
                                        <section class="quotesLeft">
                                            <div class="quotesLeftImg">
                                                <img src="~/Content/Teams/teamQuotes1.jpg">
                                            </div>
                                        </section>
                                    </article>
                                    <article class="col-7">
                                        <section class="quotesRight" style=" margin-left: 0%;">
                                            <h3>
                                                Will you get a job after Covid has wrecked Higher Education?
                                            </h3>
                                            <section class="quotesInfo">
                                                <p style="color: orange;">August 25, 2021</p>
                                                <p class="quotesInfoDetlais">
                                                    I started the Thesis Whisperer to help PhD
                                                    students finish. In the
                                                    last five years I’ve extended that mission to helping people get
                                                    jobs after they graduate.
                                                </p>
                                                <a href="https://thesiswhisperer.com/2021/08/25/will-you-get-a-job-after-covid-has-wrecked-higher-education/"
                                                   target="_blank">Visit For more</a>
                                            </section>

                                        </section>

                                    </article>


                                </section>
                            </section>

                            <section class="eachquotesSection">
                                <hr style="color:red;">
                                <section class="row">

                                    <article class="col-5">
                                        <section class="quotesLeft">
                                            <div class="quotesLeftImg">
                                                <img src="~/Content/Teams/teamQuotes2.jpg">
                                            </div>
                                        </section>
                                    </article>
                                    <article class="col-7">
                                        <section class="quotesRight" style=" margin-left: 0%;">
                                            <h3>
                                                The art of the ‘cold call’ email
                                            </h3>
                                            <section class="quotesInfo">
                                                <p style="color: orange;">July 7, 2021</p>
                                                <p class="quotesInfoDetlais">
                                                    We humans are a curious lot. We are highly
                                                    social creatures but idiosyncratic. There is a lot of love, but also
                                                    a lot of jostling.
                                                </p>
                                                <a href="https://thesiswhisperer.com/2021/07/07/cold-call-emailing/"
                                                   target="_blank">Visit For more</a>
                                            </section>

                                        </section>

                                    </article>


                                </section>
                            </section>

                            <section class="eachquotesSection">
                                <hr style="color:red;">
                                <section class="row">

                                    <article class="col-5">
                                        <section class="quotesLeft">
                                            <div class="quotesLeftImg">
                                                <img src="~/Content/Teams/teamQuotes3.jpg">
                                            </div>
                                        </section>
                                    </article>
                                    <article class="col-7">
                                        <section class="quotesRight" style=" margin-left: 0%;">
