                                                    called in Australia, a Thesis, is a very particular kind of writing
                                                    challenge.
                                                </p>
                                                <a href="https://thesiswhisperer.com/2021/05/05/how-to-make-your-dissertation-speak-to-experts/"
                                                   target="_blank">Visit For more</a>
                                            </section>

                                        </section>

                                    </article>


                                </section>
                            </section>
                        </section>

                    </section>
                    <!-- quotes Section Ends -->
                </section>
                <!-- Recent Teams ends -->
                <!-- add  starts -->
                <section class="col-3 rightPart">
                    <section class="">
                        <!-- add Part Starts  -->
                        <section class="addPart" onclick="">
                            <div class="addPartImg add-one">
                                <a href="https://thesiswhisperer.com/2021/05/05/how-to-make-your-dissertation-speak-to-experts/"
                                   target="=_blank">Add name</a>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                    </section>
                    <section class="">
                        <!-- add Part Starts  -->
                        <section class="addPart" onclick="">
                            <div class="addPartImg add-two">
                                <a href="https://thesiswhisperer.com/2021/05/05/how-to-make-your-dissertation-speak-to-experts/"
                                   target="=_blank">Add Name</a>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                    </section>
                    <section class="">
                        <!-- add Part Starts  -->
                        <section class="addPart" onclick="">
                            <div class="addPartImg add-three">
                                <a href="https://thesiswhisperer.com/2021/05/05/how-to-make-your-dissertation-speak-to-experts/ "
                                   target="=_blank">Add Name</a>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                    </section>
                </section>
                <!-- add  ends -->
            </section>

            <!--Extra Image Part Starts-->
            <section class="" style="height: 500px;">
                <img src="~/Content/Teams/robotImg.jpg" style="height: 100%; width:100%">

            </section>

            <!--Extra Image Part Ends-->
            <!-- Team Advice Starts -->
            <section class="teamAdviceSection">
                <div class="">
                    <section class="row">
                        <div class="col-6 left">
                            <figure>
                                <div class="media">
                                </div>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" version="1.1" preserveAspectRatio="none"
                                         xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                        <defs>
                                            <mask id="leftMask" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%">
                                                <rect id="alpha" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"></rect>
                                                <text class="title" dx="50%" dy="2.5em">STRONG </text>
                                                <text class="title"
                                                      dx="50%" dy="3.5em">SENSE </text>
                                            </mask>
                                        </defs>
                                        <rect id="base" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"></rect>
                                    </svg>
                                    <div class="body">
                                        <p>
                                            Team members have a strong sense of belonging to the group. They experience a
                                            deep commitment to the group’s decisions and actions.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </figcaption><a href="#"></a>
                            </figure>
                        </div>


                        <div class="col-6 right">

                            <figure>
                                <div class="media"></div>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" version="1.1" preserveAspectRatio="none"
                                         xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                        <defs>
                                            <mask id="rightMask" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%">
                                                <rect id="alpha" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"></rect>
